penClaw platform skills\"\n      /custom/: \"Custom workspace-specific skills\"\n\n  reference:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/reference\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"Curated reference: PRD summaries, architecture guides, personas\"\n      \"\": \"Curated reference: personas, architecture, installation guides\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":48,"aggregated":"global_context: |\n  OpenClaw workspace memory system with QMD integration.\n  Documents organized hierarchically: system/, projects/, daily/, skills/, reference/, context/.\n  Prioritize recent documents (2026) and active context.\n  \ncollections:\n  system:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/system\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"System configuration: OpenClaw gateway, auth tokens, model providers, cron jobs\"\n      gateway: \"Gateway settings: port 18789, local mode\"\n      cron: Cron job configuration and scheduling\n      config: OpenClaw configuration files and settings\n\n  projects:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/projects\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"Active projects: YouTube content, GitHub open source, CRM system\"\n      /youtube/: \"YouTube channel: video ideas, scripts\"\n      /github/: \"Open source projects and contributions\"\n      /crm/: \"Personal CRM: contacts, meetings, follow-ups\"\n\n  daily:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"Daily raw notes: session transcripts, decisions, tasks\"\n      /2026/: \"Year 2026 sessions - most recent and relevant\"\n      /2026/02/: \"February 2026 - high recency sessions\"\n\n  context:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/context\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"Active context: current task, session state, decisions in-flight\"\n      /active/: \"Current tasks and in-progress work - HIGH PRIORITY\"\n      /archive/: \"Completed context snapshots - historical reference\"\n\n  skills:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/skills\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"OpenClaw skills: built-in and custom\"\n      /built-in/: \"Core OpenClaw platform skills\"\n      /custom/: \"Custom workspace-specific skills\"\n\n  reference:\n    path: /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/memory/reference\n    pattern: \"**/*.md\"\n    context:\n      /: \"Curated reference: PRD summaries, architecture guides, personas\"\n      \"\": \"Curated reference: personas, architecture, installation guides\"","cwd":"/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772962551963}}
